== 賽前爆發的禁藥醜聞 ==

2016年6月，IWF公布過去兩屆奧運有12名獎牌得主涉及使用禁藥，不僅當事人面臨禁賽、追回獎牌的處分，保加利亞、哈薩克、俄羅斯、亞塞拜然隊甚至可能無緣本屆奧運。<ref name="Sky">{{cite news|title=Ten weightlifters, including great Ilya Ilyin, return positive tests from London 2012|url=http://www.skysports.com/more-sports/olympics/news/14935/10315199/ten-weightlifters-including-great-ilya-ilyin-return-positive-tests-from-london-2012|work=Sky Sports|date=15 June 2016|accessdate=2016-07-12|archive-date=2016-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160801090241/http://www.skysports.com/more-sports/olympics/news/14935/10315199/ten-weightlifters-including-great-ilya-ilyin-return-positive-tests-from-london-2012|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="IWF18June">{{cite news|title=PUBLIC DISCLOSURES|url=http://www.iwf.net/2016/06/18/public-disclosures-2/|work=IWF|date=18 June 2016|accessdate=2016-07-12|archive-date=2016-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630043712/http://www.iwf.net/2016/06/18/public-disclosures-2/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

同時本屆奧運，保加利亞因為禁藥陽性反應事件達11起而不得參與（一個代表團一年之內只容許2起禁藥事件）<ref>{{cite news|title=Bulgaria Olympic ban confirmed by Court of Arbitration for Sport|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/weightlifting/35446124|work=BBC Sport|accessdate=19 June 2016|archive-date=2016-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160828013952/http://www.bbc.com/sport/weightlifting/35446124|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而俄羅斯雖然只有2例陽性反應，但是因為涉及了117起掩飾該項運動的禁藥事件，甚至4名選手名字出現在反禁藥報告中，也在2016年7月29日宣布不得參與，並說明對於這個結果「極度震驚與失望」並稱俄羅斯使舉重運動蒙羞，因此做出這個決定來維護舉重運動的名譽。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.iwf.net/2016/07/29/iwf-eb-decision-on-russian-participation-at-the-rio-2016-og/|title=IWF decision on Russian participation in Rio 2016|publisher=[[International_Weightlifting_Federation|IWF]]|accessdate=29 July 2016|archive-date=2017-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171027095031/http://www.iwf.net/2016/07/29/iwf-eb-decision-on-russian-participation-at-the-rio-2016-og/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

